reviewText: excellent delivery time and in excellent condition, we had a most entertaining evening watching this dvd, well recommended for anyone to watch
I have lived in Australia for 12 years and you can't beat the Aussie humour. They love to laugh at themselves. This DVD is great. It encompasses the true Aussie humour.
My boyfriend loves this silly Aussie comedy he never stops laughing when he watches it!!! Great quality DVD set thanks :)
